This is where grandpa left.

280
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:02,320
Good memory.

281
00:21:03,984 --> 00:21:05,136
That's right.

282
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:14,960
Grandma, they said you're very sick.

283
00:21:18,208 --> 00:21:19,312
Are you afraid?

284
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:23,696
Yezi.

285
00:21:24,864 --> 00:21:26,640
In this world,

286
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:30,800
There's nothing that humans can't figure out.

287
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:37,616
Except one. That no one has figured out before.

288
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:44,816
