297
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:22,144
People will come and tell you,
you need to do this, do that.

298
00:22:22,672 --> 00:22:26,416
To make you become sophisticated.

299
00:22:27,184 --> 00:22:31,184
They say that will help you in this world.

300
00:22:32,912 --> 00:22:34,272
Just tell them,

301
00:22:34,672 --> 00:22:36,112
Get the hell out.

302
00:22:39,488 --> 00:22:41,872
If growing up means to be sophisticated.

303
00:22:43,904 --> 00:22:46,736
I'd rather you'll be a kid forever.

304
00:22:47,536 --> 00:22:49,008
Like now.

305
00:22:50,080 --> 00:22:53,904
A pure and innocent little girl.

306
00:23:13,344 --> 00:23:14,672
Yezi.

307
00:23:16,336 --> 00:23:19,552
