and the most beautiful girl in the world.

320
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:13,520
But because of that,

321
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:17,392
many people were jealous of her. Especially that witch.

322
00:24:18,110 --> 00:24:20,784
So she sent some men to kill her.

323
00:24:21,872 --> 00:24:23,456
But they couldn't.

324
00:24:24,448 --> 00:24:26,448
Because she had a good fate.

325
00:24:27,392 --> 00:24:28,848
She was very powerful.

326
00:24:29,072 --> 00:24:31,664
Many people loves her.

327
00:24:31,740 --> 00:24:33,456
Every people who saw her.

328
00:24:34,864 --> 00:24:35,920
But...

329
00:24:36,576 --> 00:24:38,768
Me and grandma were sitting there for a long time.

330
00:24:38,944 --> 00:24:42,416
Until Liao Danyi and his dad came to the beach.

331
00:24:56,512 --> 00:24:57,968
After you found my mom,

332
00:24:57,968 --> 00:24:59,728
why you didn't tell us?

333
00:25:00,912 --> 00:25:03,984
Grandma said, she doesn't want you to know.

334
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:06,816
