335
00:25:07,696 --> 00:25:09,168
This is your friend?

336
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:13,808
Little girl, listen.

337
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,728
This isn't over.

338
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:19,024
But first, you need to stay away from my family as from now!

339
00:25:25,856 --> 00:25:26,672
Danyi!

340
00:26:06,288 --> 00:26:09,696
Several weeks after that thing,

341
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:16,000
