Although he is a governor.

343
00:26:44,112 --> 00:26:45,472
Looks so careless.

344
00:26:46,016 --> 00:26:47,904
But in fact, he is a hero.

345
00:27:16,192 --> 00:27:18,320
That's so beautiful! Okay!

346
00:27:46,464 --> 00:27:47,456
This way, this way.

347
00:27:47,584 --> 00:27:48,944
Kill him, kill him.

348
00:27:49,728 --> 00:27:50,592
Go!

